data.description: Welcome Home to what locals call "Our Little Slice of Paradise." This home has been completely remodeled and now has a Private Pool with beautiful water features and a dog run. It has a new roof as of 5/1/23. The downstairs has a wonderful Open Floor plan which includes a beautiful fireplace with views of the pool, wonderful new large windows, and soaring ceilings. The kitchen includes a center island, a wine refrigerator, Farmhouse sink, and Pantry. There is a Bedroom En-suite downstairs, perfect for guests. The salt water pool is so inviting with two sitting areas, a firepit area, beautiful landscaping and a new fence. Clear Lake Shores is a Golfcart Community with a year-round social schedule. Purchasing a home here is not just buying a house, it's a way of life.
